data.description:
Your quest for the perfect home ends here! This remarkable property offers unparalleled value that will leave you in awe. With a new HVAC unit installed in 2016 and a roof replacement in 2017 backed by a 15-year transferable warranty, peace of mind is guaranteed. Enjoy the luxury of a private backyard, shielded from prying eyes with no direct neighbors behind you, and the added bonus of cable included in your HOA fee.
Unwind by the glistening community pool, then find serenity in your backyard oasis shaded by mature trees, including two orange and one lemon tree. Inside, the spacious open-concept living area is bathed in natural light thanks to vaulted ceilings. Each bedroom boasts these lofty ceilings, while the primary bedroom boasts a substantial walk-in closet.
